headline: Behavox Expands Google Cloud Partnership with $42 Million Investment to Deliver AI Solutions in Financial Services
summary: LONDON & MONTREAL, October 02, 2025--Behavox, the AI company that transforms data into insights to safeguard and enhance businesses, today announced a $42 million investment in Google Cloud infrastructure and services as part of its expanded strategic partnership.

headline: 1 Volatile Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 We Question
summary: Volatility cuts both ways - while it creates opportunities, it also increases risk, making sharp declines just as likely as big gains. This unpredictability can shake out even the most experienced investors.
